'''乳糜瀉'''（{{lang-en|coeliac disease}} 或 celiac disease）是主要會影響到[[小腸|小腸]]的長期[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]<ref name="NIH2015">{{cite web|title=Celiac Disease|url=http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/celiac-disease/Pages/facts.aspx|accessdate=17 March 2016|date=June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616124057/http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/celiac-disease/Pages/facts.aspx|archivedate=2016-06-16|website=NIDDKD|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典型的症狀包含胃腸道症狀，像是慢性[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、{{le|腹脹|abdominal distention}}、{{le|吸收不良|malabsorption}}、降低食慾，以及使孩童{{tsl|en|failure to thrive|生長遲緩|}}<ref name="Fasano2005Pediatric">{{cite journal|title=Clinical presentation of celiac disease in the pediatric population|author=Fasano A|date=April 2005|journal=Gastroenterology|issue=4 Suppl 1|doi=10.1053/j.gastro.2005.02.015|volume=128|pages=S68–73|type=Review|pmid=15825129}}</ref>。這個病通常發生在六個月大到兩歲之間<ref name="Fasano2005Pediatric" />。不典型的症狀比較常見，尤其是病人年紀大於兩歲時<ref name="ESPGHAN2012">{{cite journal|title=European Society for Pediatric Gastroenterology, Hepatology, and Nutrition guidelines for the diagnosis of coeliac disease|url=http://www.espghan.org/fileadmin/user_upload/guidelines_pdf/Guidelines_2404/European_Society_for_Pediatric_Gastroenterology_.28__1_.pdf|date=January 2012|journal=J Pediatr Gastroenterol Nutr|issue=1|doi=10.1097/MPG.0b013e31821a23d0|volume=54|pages=136–60|type=Practice Guideline|pmid=22197856|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403065800/http://www.espghan.org/fileadmin/user_upload/guidelines_pdf/Guidelines_2404/European_Society_for_Pediatric_Gastroenterology_.28__1_.pdf|archivedate=2016-04-03|quote=Since 1990, the understanding of the pathological processes of CD has increased enormously, leading to a change in the clinical paradigm of CD from a chronic, gluten-dependent enteropathy of childhood to a systemic disease with chronic immune features affecting different organ systems. (...) atypical symptoms may be considerably more common than classic symptoms|vauthors=Husby S, Koletzko S, Korponay-Szabó IR, Mearin ML, Phillips A, Shamir R, Troncone R, Giersiepen K, Branski D, Catassi C, Lelgeman M, Mäki M, Ribes-Koninckx C, Ventura A, Zimmer KP,(( ESPGHAN Working Group on Coeliac Disease Diagnosis; ESPGHAN Gastroenterology Committee; European Society for Pediatric Gastroenterology, Hepatology, and Nutrition))|access-date=2018-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Newnham2017">{{cite journal|title=Coeliac disease in the 21st century: Paradigm shifts in the modern age|first1=Evan D|journal=Journal of Gastroenterology and Hepatology|doi=10.1111/jgh.13704|year=2017|volume=32|pages=82–85|pmid=28244672|quote=Presentation of CD with malabsorptive symptoms or malnutrition is now the exception rather than the rule.|last1=Newnham}}{{free access}}</ref><ref name="TonuttiBizzaro2014">{{cite journal|title=Diagnosis and classification of celiac disease and gluten sensitivity|date=2014|journal=Autoimmun Rev|issue=4–5|doi=10.1016/j.autrev.2014.01.043|volume=13|pages=472–6|pmid=24440147|vauthors=Tonutti E, Bizzaro N}}</ref>。腸胃道症狀可能輕微或沒有表現，另外也可能會有許多{{tsl|en|systemic disease|全身性疾病|症狀影響到身體任何部位}}，或甚至是沒有顯著症狀表現<ref name="Fasano2005Pediatric" />。乳糜瀉剛開始是被發現於孩童身上<ref name="Cic2015">{{cite journal|title=The Spectrum of Differences between Childhood and Adulthood Celiac Disease|date=22 October 2015|journal=Nutrients|issue=10|doi=10.3390/nu7105426|volume=7|pages=8733–51|type=Review|pmc=4632446|pmid=26506381|quote=Several additional studies in extensive series of coeliac patients have clearly shown that TG2A sensitivity varies depending on the severity of duodenal damage, and reaches almost 100% in the presence of complete villous atrophy (more common in children under three years), 70% for subtotal atrophy, and up to 30% when only an increase in IELs is present. ''(IELs: intraepithelial lymphocytes)''|vauthors=Ciccocioppo R, Kruzliak P, Cangemi GC, Pohanka M, Betti E, Lauret E, Rodrigo L}}</ref><ref name="ESPGHAN2012" />，但其實任意年紀都可以發病<ref name="Fasano2005Pediatric" /><ref name="ESPGHAN2012" />。此病常常和其他[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]共病，如[[1型糖尿病|1型糖尿病]]和[[甲状腺炎|甲狀腺炎]]等<ref name="Cic2015" />。

==机制==
乳糜瀉是因人體不適應麩質進而引發過敏反應的結果。麩質是[[小麥|小麥]]、[[大麥|大麥]]及[[裸麥|裸麥]]等穀物含有的一組蛋白質<ref name="TovoliMasi2015">{{cite journal|title=Clinical and diagnostic aspects of gluten related disorders|date=March 2015|journal=World Journal of Clinical Cases|issue=3|doi=10.12998/wjcc.v3.i3.275|volume=3|pages=275–84|type=Review|pmc=4360499|pmid=25789300|vauthors=Tovoli F, Masi C, Guidetti E, Negrini G, Paterini P, Bolondi L}}</ref><ref name="PenaginiDilillo2013">{{cite journal|title=Gluten-free diet in children: an approach to a nutritionally adequate and balanced diet|date=November 2013|journal=Nutrients|issue=11|doi=10.3390/nu5114553|volume=5|pages=4553–65|type=Review|pmc=3847748|pmid=24253052|vauthors=Penagini F, Dilillo D, Meneghin F, Mameli C, Fabiano V, Zuccotti GV}}</ref><ref name="Lancet2009">{{cite journal|title=Coeliac disease|date=April 2009|journal=Lancet|issue=9673|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(09)60254-3|volume=373|pages=1480–93|pmid=19394538|vauthors=Di Sabatino A, Corazza GR}}</ref>。一般而言，適量的食用燕麥若無與摻混其他含有麩質的穀物，通常不會對患者造成影響<ref name="PenaginiDilillo2013" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Safety of Adding Oats to a Gluten-Free Diet for Patients With Celiac Disease: Systematic Review and Meta-analysis of Clinical and Observational Studies|url=http://eprints.whiterose.ac.uk/115341/1/FordSafety%20of%20Adding%20Oats.pdf|date=August 2017|journal=Gastroenterology|issue=2|doi=10.1053/j.gastro.2017.04.009|volume=153|pages=395–409.e3|pmid=28431885|vauthors=Pinto-Sánchez MI, Causada-Calo N, Bercik P, Ford AC, Murray JA, Armstrong D, Semrad C, Kupfer SS, Alaedini A, Moayyedi P, Leffler DA, Verdú EF, Green P|access-date=2020-02-20|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129071334/http://eprints.whiterose.ac.uk/115341/1/FordSafety%20of%20Adding%20Oats.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而食用後會出現乳糜瀉問題的機率則可能與於燕麥的[[栽培品种|品種]]有關<ref name="PenaginiDilillo2013" /><ref name="CominoMoreno2015">{{cite journal|title=Role of oats in celiac disease|date=November 2015|journal=World Journal of Gastroenterology|issue=41|doi=10.3748/wjg.v21.i41.11825|volume=21|pages=11825–31|pmc=4631980|pmid=26557006|quote=It is necessary to consider that oats include many varieties, containing various amino acid sequences and showing different immunoreactivities associated with toxic prolamins. As a result, several studies have shown that the immunogenicity of oats varies depending on the cultivar consumed. Thus, it is essential to thoroughly study the variety of oats used in a food ingredient before including it in a gluten-free diet.|vauthors=Comino I, Moreno M, Sousa C}}</ref>。

此症是遺傳性疾病<ref name="NIH2015" />，患者攝取到麩質後，身體裡的異常免疫系統對此產生反應，並可能導致生成數種[[自身抗體|自身抗體]]而影響許多不同的器官<ref name="Lund2015">{{cite journal|title=Coeliac disease and autoimmune disease-genetic overlap and screening|date=September 2015|journal=Nature Reviews. Gastroenterology & Hepatology|issue=9|doi=10.1038/nrgastro.2015.136|volume=12|pages=507–15|type=Review|pmid=26303674|quote=The abnormal immunological response elicited by gluten-derived proteins can lead to the production of several different autoantibodies, which affect different systems.|vauthors=Lundin KE, Wijmenga C}}</ref><ref name="NICEcoeliac">{{NICE|86|Recognition and assessment of coeliac disease|2015}}</ref>。在小腸中，自身抗體會引發炎症反應，並可能造成生長於小腸內壁的[[肠绒毛|絨毛]]長度變短（絨毛萎縮）<ref name=NIH2015/><ref name=VivasVaquero2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Vivas S, Vaquero L, Rodríguez-Martín L, Caminero A | title = Age-related differences in celiac disease: Specific characteristics of adult presentation | journal = World Journal of Gastrointestinal Pharmacology and Therapeutics | volume = 6 | issue = 4 | pages = 207–12 | date = November 2015 | pmid = 26558154 | pmc = 4635160 | doi = 10.4292/wjgpt.v6.i4.207 | type = Review | quote = In addition, the presence of intraepithelial lymphocytosis and/or villous atrophy and crypt hyperplasia of small-bowel mucosa, and clinical remission after withdrawal of gluten from the diet, are also used for diagnosis antitransglutaminase antibody (tTGA) titers and the degree of histological lesions inversely correlate with age. Thus, as the age of diagnosis increases antibody titers decrease and histological damage is less marked. It is common to find adults without villous atrophy showing only an inflammatory pattern in duodenal mucosa biopsies: Lymphocytic enteritis (Marsh I) or added crypt hyperplasia (Marsh II) }}</ref>，而這會影響營養吸收，患者因而經常[[貧血|貧血]]<ref name="NIH2015" /><ref name="Lancet2009" />。

==诊断==
[[诊断|确诊]]通常非常困难，大部分患者在正确诊断前都经歷较长的时间<ref name=MatthiasPfeiffer2010>{{cite journal|vauthors=Matthias T, Pfeiffer S, Selmi C, Eric Gershwin M|title=Diagnostic challenges in celiac disease and the role of the tissue transglutaminase-neo-epitope|journal=Clin Rev Allergy Immunol|volume=38|issue=2–3|pages=298–301|date=2010年4月|pmid=19629760|doi=10.1007/s12016-009-8160-z|type=Review}}</ref>。现在有多个检测手段可以使用。患者症状的严重程度可能决定了这些检测的顺序，但如果患者已经在进行[[无麸质饮食|无麸质饮食]]，则'''所有'''上述的检测都无效。[[小肠|小肠]]的损伤通常在饮食中去掉麸质后几周开始恢复，而[[抗体|抗体]]的水平也在数月后下降。对于那些正在进行无麸质饮食的人群，可能需要在其饮食中每日有一餐加入含麸质的食物，持续六周后再进行检测。<ref name="NICEcoeliac"/>

診斷一般是透過血液抗體測試及腸道[[活體組織切片|活體組織]]切片進行，會用特殊的[[基因檢測|基因檢測]]作為輔助<ref name="NIH2015" />。不過診斷不容易直接進行<ref name=MatthiasPfeiffer2010 />，多半血液中的抗體檢驗是陰性的<ref name=LewisScott2006>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lewis NR, Scott BB | title = Systematic review: the use of serology to exclude or diagnose coeliac disease (a comparison of the endomysial and tissue transglutaminase antibody tests) | journal = Alimentary Pharmacology & Therapeutics | volume = 24 | issue = 1 | pages = 47–54 | date = July 2006 | pmid = 16803602 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2036.2006.02967.x }}</ref><ref name=AGA2006 />，而腸道健康的絨毛也只有少許變化<ref name=MolinaInfanteSantolaria2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Molina-Infante J, Santolaria S, Sanders DS, Fernández-Bañares F | title = Systematic review: noncoeliac gluten sensitivity | journal = Alimentary Pharmacology & Therapeutics | volume = 41 | issue = 9 | pages = 807–20 | date = May 2015 | pmid = 25753138 | doi = 10.1111/apt.13155 | type = Review | quote = Furthermore, seronegativity is more common in coeliac disease patients without villous atrophy (Marsh 1-2 lesions), but these ‘minor’ forms of coeliac disease may have similar clinical manifestations to those with villous atrophy and may show similar clinical–histological remission with reversal of haematological or biochemical disturbances on a gluten-free diet (GFD). }}</ref>。病患在確診前多半已有嚴重症狀，且持續了幾年<ref name=CichewiczMearns2019 /><ref name=LudvigssonCard2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ludvigsson JF, Card T, Ciclitira PJ, Swift GL, Nasr I, Sanders DS, Ciacci C | title = Support for patients with celiac disease: A literature review | journal = United European Gastroenterology Journal | volume = 3 | issue = 2 | pages = 146–59 | date = April 2015 | pmid = 25922674 | pmc = 4406900 | doi = 10.1177/2050640614562599 | type = Review }}</ref>。目前越來越多的確診案例來自於[[無症狀|無症狀]]患者的{{le|篩檢|screening}}結果<ref name="VanHeelWest">{{cite journal | vauthors = van Heel DA, West J | title = Recent advances in coeliac disease | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_gut_2006-07_55_7/page/1037 | journal = Gut | volume = 55 | issue = 7 | pages = 1037–46 | date = July 2006 | pmid = 16766754 | pmc = 1856316 | doi = 10.1136/gut.2005.075119 | type = Review }}</ref>。不過目前尚無足夠實證佐證篩檢的效果<ref name=USPSTF2017>{{cite journal | vauthors = Bibbins-Domingo K, Grossman DC, Curry SJ, Barry MJ, Davidson KW, Doubeni CA, Ebell M, Epling JW, Herzstein J, Kemper AR, Krist AH, Kurth AE, Landefeld CS, Mangione CM, Phipps MG, Silverstein M, Simon MA, Tseng CW | title = Screening for Celiac Disease: US Preventive Services Task Force Recommendation Statement | journal = JAMA | volume = 317 | issue = 12 | pages = 1252–1257 | date = March 2017 | pmid = 28350936 | doi = 10.1001/jama.2017.1462 }}</ref>。此病症是由對於麩質蛋白質的永久不耐所造成<ref name=NIH2015/>，和更罕見的{{le|小麥過敏|wheat allergy}}不同<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Burkhardt |first1=J. G. |last2=Chapa-Rodriguez |first2=A. |last3=Bahna |first3=S. L. |title=Gluten sensitivities and the allergist: Threshing the grain from the husks |journal=Allergy |date=July 2018 |volume=73 |issue=7 |pages=1359–1368 |doi=10.1111/all.13354 |pmid=29131356}}</ref>。

==治疗==
目前認為對此病唯一有效的治療方式是讓病患採取嚴格的終生[[无麸质饮食|無麩質飲食]]。這樣可讓大多數的患者腸粘膜復元、改善症狀並降低產生併發症的風險<ref name="SeeKaukinen2015">{{cite journal|title=Practical insights into gluten-free diets|date=2015年10月|journal=Nat Rev Gastroenterol Hepatol|issue=10|doi=10.1038/nrgastro.2015.156|volume=12|pages=580–91|type=Review|pmid=26392070|quote=A lack of symptoms and/or negative serological markers are not reliable indicators of mucosal response to the diet. Furthermore, up to 30% of patients continue to have gastrointestinal symptoms despite a strict GFD.122,124 If adherence is questioned, a structured interview by a qualified dietitian can help to identify both intentional and inadvertent sources of gluten.|vauthors=See JA, Kaukinen K, Makharia GK, Gibson PR, Murray JA}}</ref>。如果不加以治療，此病將可能導致如腸道[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]等[[癌症|癌症]]，並會略為增加早期死亡的風險<ref name=Leb2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lebwohl B, Ludvigsson JF, Green PH | title = Celiac disease and non-celiac gluten sensitivity | journal = BMJ | volume = 351 | pages = h4347 | date = October 2015 | pmid = 26438584 | pmc = 4596973 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.h4347 | quote = Celiac disease occurs in about 1% of the population worldwide, although most people with the condition are undiagnosed. It can cause a wide variety of symptoms, both intestinal and extra-intestinal because it is a systemic autoimmune disease that is triggered by dietary gluten. Patients with coeliac disease are at increased risk of cancer, including a twofold to fourfold increased risk of non-Hodgkin’s lymphoma and a more than 30-fold increased risk of small intestinal adenocarcinoma, and they have a 1.4-fold increased risk of death. | type = Review }}</ref>。世界各地罹患此病的人口比率各不相同，從1/300人至1/40不等，平均則是約在1/100至1/170間<ref name=NEJM2012>{{cite journal | vauthors = Fasano A, Catassi C | title = Clinical practice. Celiac disease | journal = The New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 367 | issue = 25 | pages = 2419–26 | date = December 2012 | pmid = 23252527 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMcp1113994 | type = Review }}</ref>。據估計，罹有此病者中有高達80％並未被確診出來，通常是因為他們的胃腸道症狀極為輕微或根本沒有出現症狀，以及因為大眾缺乏對於症狀和診斷標準的知識所致<ref name=WGO2016 >{{cite web|url=http://www.worldgastroenterology.org/guidelines/global-guidelines/celiac-disease/celiac-disease-english|title=Celiac disease|date=July 2016|publisher={{tsl|en|World Gastroenterology Organisation||World Gastroenterology Organisation}} Global Guidelines|accessdate=23 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317123604/http://www.worldgastroenterology.org/guidelines/global-guidelines/celiac-disease/celiac-disease-english|archivedate=2017-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CichewiczMearns2019>{{cite journal| vauthors=Cichewicz AB, Mearns ES, Taylor A, Boulanger T, Gerber M, Leffler DA | display-authors=etal | title=Diagnosis and Treatment Patterns in Celiac Disease | journal=Dig Dis Sci | volume=64 | issue=8 | pages=2095–2106 | year= 1 March 2019 | pmid=30820708 | doi=10.1007/s10620-019-05528-3 | type=Review }} </ref><ref name=LionettiGatti2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lionetti E, Gatti S, Pulvirenti A, Catassi C | title = Celiac disease from a global perspective | journal = Best Practice & Research. Clinical Gastroenterology | volume = 29 | issue = 3 | pages = 365–79 | date = June 2015 | pmid = 26060103 | doi = 10.1016/j.bpg.2015.05.004 | type = Review }}</ref>。統計上，此病的女性患者較男性略多一些<ref name=His2006>{{cite journal | vauthors = Hischenhuber C, Crevel R, Jarry B, Mäki M, Moneret-Vautrin DA, Romano A, Troncone R, Ward R | title = Review article: safe amounts of gluten for patients with wheat allergy or coeliac disease | journal = Alimentary Pharmacology & Therapeutics | volume = 23 | issue = 5 | pages = 559–75 | date = March 2006 | pmid = 16480395 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2036.2006.02768.x }}</ref>。

